product.name: بكج عطور نسائية
product.description: بكج عطور نسائي فاخر يجمع أرقى النغمات التي تعكس قوة الأنوثة ورقتها. توليفة ساحرة من الروائح الزهرية والفاكهية واللمسات الشرقية الراقية، صُممت لترافقك في كل لحظة وتمنحك حضوراً يلفت الأنظار أينما كنت. هدية مثالية لكل امرأة تعشق الفخامة وتستحق التميز.

product.name: Foam balls & Feathers for All Pets!
product.description: Bring endless fun to your pets with this playful mix of foam balls and colorful feathers! Designed for all types of pets, these lightweight toys are easy to carry, chase, toss, and bat around. The foam balls are soft, safe, and gentle on paws and teeth, while the feathers add an exciting flutter that captures attention instantly. Perfect for encouraging natural hunting instincts, reducing boredom, and keeping your pet active throughout the day. Whether you have a cat, small dog, or playful little pet, this toy set offers safe, engaging entertainment that sparks curiosity and movement. A simple way to add joy and enrichment to your pet’s daily routine.

product.name: Cat Dry Food - 1.3 Kg
product.description: This premium dry cat food is crafted to support your cat’s overall health with high-quality, natural ingredients. Made from real protein as the first ingredient, it delivers balanced nutrition that helps maintain strong muscles, healthy digestion, and sustained energy. The recipe is free from artificial colors, preservatives, and flavor enhancers, ensuring a clean and wholesome meal in every bowl. It’s also grain-free, making it an excellent choice for cats with sensitive stomachs or food intolerance. Packed with essential vitamins, minerals, and omega fatty acids, this formula promotes a shiny coat, strong immunity, and long-term wellness. A simple, nutritious, and trustworthy choice for your cat’s daily diet.
